        "posted_at": "2026-03-14T12:07:44.340Z"
      },
      {
        "text": "Discipline isn't about being perfect, it's about being persistent. Even when no one is watching, you're still accountable to yourself.",
        "tone": "empathetic",
        "format": "quote-style",
        "pillar": [
          "discipline"
        ],
        "trigger": "reframe",
        "posted_at": "2026-03-14T12:07:44.340Z"
      },
      {
        "text": "It's okay to not have it all together. You can start building consistency even when life is chaotic. I'm still trying to fix my sleep schedule, but every small win counts.",
